<div class="homepage wrapper">

  <div class="slideshow">
     <div>
       <div class="text">
         <h2 class="hidden">A TRIP DOWN MEMORY LANE<br>IN SAIGON</h2>
         <div class="innertext hidden">
           <div class="seperator"></div>
           <p>Unforgetable experience to grasp all that Saigon has to offer:</p>
           <p>heritage, culture, food, nightlife and much more</p>
         </div>
       </div>
       <div class="image">
         <%= image_tag 'n1.jpg' %>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div>
       <div class="text">
         <h2 class="hidden">DISCOVER THE UNSEEN<br>THE LESS TRAVELLED</h2>
         <div class="innertext hidden">
           <div class="seperator"></div>
           <p>Unforgetable experience to grasp all that Saigon has to offer:</p>
           <p>heritage, culture, food, nightlife and much more</p>
         </div>
       </div>
       <div class="image">
         <%= image_tag 'n11.jpg' %>
      </div>
     </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row introduction">
    <div class="book_now">
      BOOK YOUR TRIP!
    </div>
    <div class="col-6 introduction">
      <h2>MÉMOIRES DE SAIGON</h2>
      <div class="seperator"></div>
      <p>
        A friendly boutique hotel located right in the heart of District 1, Ho Chi Minh City, only 1 km from Ben Thanh Market and 500m from Bui Vien – the best nightlife hub in town. It is also only a few minutes’ walk away from other popular attractions. Situated in a quiet street off the main road, Mémoires de Saigon offers a soothing night sleep after your strenuous journeys. Don’t forget to also check out various food outlets, cafes, gyms, spas and convenience stores just around the corner.
      </p>
      <div class="timeandweather">
        <div class="weather">
          <div class="icon">
            <!-- Generated by IcoMoon.io -->
            <svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
            <title>cloud</title>
            <path d="M32 20.548c0-2.565-1.771-4.716-4.156-5.296-0.101-4.022-3.389-7.252-7.433-7.252-2.369 0-4.477 1.109-5.839 2.835-0.764-0.987-1.959-1.624-3.303-1.624-2.307 0-4.176 1.871-4.176 4.179 0 0.201 0.015 0.399 0.043 0.592-0.351-0.063-0.711-0.098-1.080-0.098-3.344-0-6.054 2.712-6.054 6.058s2.71 6.058 6.054 6.058l20.508-0c3.004-0.006 5.438-2.444 5.438-5.451z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p><%= get_temp %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="time">
          <div class="icon">
            <!-- Generated by IcoMoon.io -->
            <svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
            <title>clock</title>
            <path d="M20.586 23.414l-6.586-6.586v-8.828h4v7.172l5.414 5.414zM16 0c-8.837 0-16 7.163-16 16s7.163 16 16 16 16-7.163 16-16-7.163-16-16-16zM16 28c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12s5.373-12 12-12c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12s-5.373 12-12 12z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p><%= get_time %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-6 booking">
      <%= simple_form_for :reservation, url: choose_your_room_path do |f| %>
        <%= f.input :arrival_date, as: 'hidden', input_html: {value: get_timestamp_now} %>
        <%= f.input :departure_date, as: 'hidden', input_html: {value: get_timestamp_tomorrow} %>
        <%= f.input :guests, as: 'hidden', input_html: {value: 1} %>
      <% end %>
      <div class="booking infos">
        <div class="arrival info">
          <h2>ARRIVING</h2>
          <div class="value arrival">
            <div class="month"></div>
            <div class="date"></div>
            <div class="popup-icon">
              <!-- Generated by IcoMoon.io -->
              <svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="28" viewBox="0 0 18 28">
              <title>angle-down</title>
              <path d="M16.797 11.5c0 0.125-0.063 0.266-0.156 0.359l-7.281 7.281c-0.094 0.094-0.234 0.156-0.359 0.156s-0.266-0.063-0.359-0.156l-7.281-7.281c-0.094-0.094-0.156-0.234-0.156-0.359s0.063-0.266 0.156-0.359l0.781-0.781c0.094-0.094 0.219-0.156 0.359-0.156 0.125 0 0.266 0.063 0.359 0.156l6.141 6.141 6.141-6.141c0.094-0.094 0.234-0.156 0.359-0.156s0.266 0.063 0.359 0.156l0.781 0.781c0.094 0.094 0.156 0.234 0.156 0.359z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="date-picker" id="arrival_date_picker"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="departure info">
          <h2>DEPARTING</h2>
          <div class="value departure">
            <div class="month"></div>
            <div class="date"></div>
            <div class="popup-icon">
              <!-- Generated by IcoMoon.io -->
              <svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="28" viewBox="0 0 18 28">
              <title>angle-down</title>
              <path d="M16.797 11.5c0 0.125-0.063 0.266-0.156 0.359l-7.281 7.281c-0.094 0.094-0.234 0.156-0.359 0.156s-0.266-0.063-0.359-0.156l-7.281-7.281c-0.094-0.094-0.156-0.234-0.156-0.359s0.063-0.266 0.156-0.359l0.781-0.781c0.094-0.094 0.219-0.156 0.359-0.156 0.125 0 0.266 0.063 0.359 0.156l6.141 6.141 6.141-6.141c0.094-0.094 0.234-0.156 0.359-0.156s0.266 0.063 0.359 0.156l0.781 0.781c0.094 0.094 0.156 0.234 0.156 0.359z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="date-picker" id="departure_date_picker"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="guests info">
          <h2>GUESTS</h2>
          <div class="value">
            <div class="popup-icon up">
              <!-- Generated by IcoMoon.io -->
              <svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="28" viewBox="0 0 18 28">
              <title>angle-up</title>
              <path d="M16.797 18.5c0 0.125-0.063 0.266-0.156 0.359l-0.781 0.781c-0.094 0.094-0.219 0.156-0.359 0.156-0.125 0-0.266-0.063-0.359-0.156l-6.141-6.141-6.141 6.141c-0.094 0.094-0.234 0.156-0.359 0.156s-0.266-0.063-0.359-0.156l-0.781-0.781c-0.094-0.094-0.156-0.234-0.156-0.359s0.063-0.266 0.156-0.359l7.281-7.281c0.094-0.094 0.234-0.156 0.359-0.156s0.266 0.063 0.359 0.156l7.281 7.281c0.094 0.094 0.156 0.234 0.156 0.359z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="people"></div>
            <div class="popup-icon">
              <!-- Generated by IcoMoon.io -->
              <svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="28" viewBox="0 0 18 28">
              <title>angle-down</title>
              <path d="M16.797 11.5c0 0.125-0.063 0.266-0.156 0.359l-7.281 7.281c-0.094 0.094-0.234 0.156-0.359 0.156s-0.266-0.063-0.359-0.156l-7.281-7.281c-0.094-0.094-0.156-0.234-0.156-0.359s0.063-0.266 0.156-0.359l0.781-0.781c0.094-0.094 0.219-0.156 0.359-0.156 0.125 0 0.266 0.063 0.359 0.156l6.141 6.141 6.141-6.141c0.094-0.094 0.234-0.156 0.359-0.156s0.266 0.063 0.359 0.156l0.781 0.781c0.094 0.094 0.156 0.234 0.156 0.359z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="number-picker">
            <div class="active" value="1">1</div>
            <div value="2">2</div>
            <div value="3">3</div>
            <div value="4">4</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="submit_button_and_hotline">
        <div class="reservation submit">
          MAKE A RESERVATION
        </div>
        <div class="hotline">
          <h2>RESERVATION HOTLINE</h2>
          <h2>+02 866.799.191</h2>
          <p>Reservation assistance available 24 hours</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row rooms">
    <% @rooms.each do |room| %>
      <%= render 'room', room: room %>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="row indulge">
    <h2>INDULGE IN THE VERY HEART OF SAIGON</h2>
    <div class="seperator"></div>
    <p>
      Travel in style as far as your desire goes.
    </p>
    <p>
      Feel like home in our mini studios, feel loved in romantic suits or be wild with our friendly capsules.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="row event">
    <div class="heading">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h2>EVENTS</h2>
        <div class="seperator"></div>
        <p>Life is too short for boredom. Explore these upcoming special events in Saigon that you wouldn’t want to be missing out on.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="events">
      <% @events.each do |event| %>
        <%= render 'event', event: event %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row gallery">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="heading">
        <h2>GALLERY</h2>
        <div class="seperator"></div>
        <p>
          Discover our hotel through this latest gallery. Taken and frequently-updated straight from our hotel.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div id="gallery">
        <div>
          <img src="/assets/n12.jpg">
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/assets/n4.JPG">
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/assets/n2.jpg">
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/assets/g8.jpg">
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/assets/n6.JPG">
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/assets/n5.JPG">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
